{"tid":143293,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔準諗，即刻答]脆香雞翼定胡南土匪雞翼","createTime":"2017-03-04T13:33:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-05T15:50:09.000Z","uid":1858,"like":215,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8042bb742211aeec939ad13ab520eb74289c35fa","tid":143293,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:33:20.000Z","msg":"啱啱人生第一次食左譚仔土匪雞翼，成日見人吹奏，食落覺得不外如是。味道可以嘅，但質感對比番m記脆香雞翼即刻分曬高低<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：脆香雞翼<br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：土匪雞翼"},{"pid":"90a5e65227f8300a7298779ee6e440521c1719fe","tid":143293,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:37:36.000Z","msg":"一定係M記啦"},{"pid":"f2f4cdf7f60c04e1588ed0e6467511d917ac72d4","tid":143293,"uid":20386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:39:40.000Z","msg":"脆香雞翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6240bed527b64b011be3dbb0193b62816b2673c1","tid":143293,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:45:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定係M記啦</blockquote><br />\n脆香雞陣味，再加埋個厚實質感真係天下無敵。如果係即炸，熱食，果d汁簡直係錦上添花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係都未必不敗，試過有兩次叫外賣班仆街唔知趕定點，炸到燶左，炸皮上面有少少黑點，但個陣味足以搞到成隻雞翼難食十萬倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ce7f2767b5d95cff42ca4bf6841545d41a4827","tid":143293,"uid":1858,