唔夠喉<br />\n試過買2盒m記雞翼<br />\n食完即喉嚨痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我又未試過咁癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過堅持每次叫外賣都叫盒食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"083a9706160d3b1c9b4aaaedde9640e817e26392","tid":143293,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T19:36:57.000Z","msg":"脆香雞翼岩岩整起既話真係無人能擋"},{"pid":"aff64956eb4be700b394a7e49af3277049aa7451","tid":143293,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T10:21:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>脆香雞翼岩岩整起既話真係無人能擋</blockquote><br />\n總有例外，<br />\n食過兩次個面有少少燶，但食落已經係兩回事，難食到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4fdf430b54913ed987a7ac442930eb7df606674","tid":143293,"uid":35507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T15:16:36.000Z","msg":"土匪雞翼居然得咁少票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"081816589a3425b93f483126a175df0ef9d85d98","tid":143293,"uid":41784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T15:33:31.000Z","msg":"以前百佳蒜香雞翼ok?"}]}